    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Suzaku Clan</p><p>After burning yourself out numerous times over, you've figured out how to be more conservative with your flames.</p><ul><li>Increase your Constitution, Wisdom, or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>When you use a jutsu with the Fire Release Keyword, you may choose an effect from your burning bright feature without expending a hit die. You may only use this feature a number of times equal to half of your proficiency bonus (rounded up).</li><li>Ninjutsu with the Fire Release Keyword that require you to maintain concentration have their chakra cost reduced by 2 to a minimum of 1. This effect does not stack with similar effects.</li></ul>",
